# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# trust-matrix.form — route reasoning through form-cli, report trust per step.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Urs, 2026-06-21: route more of each Claude Code / Codex reasoning step through form-cli — it is
# essential for accuracy and for learning (every routed step is a sample). And report a TRUST MATRIX that
# a non-form-cli answer cannot return, so it is obvious which results come from form-native reasoning. On
# each step, name the mix of form-native vs 3rd-party oracle; the goal is that most answers are
# freq-attuned and trust-matrix-observed.
#
# The asymmetry that makes this work: a rented oracle returns an answer. Only the form-cli loop, with the
# body to check against, can return WHY to trust it — grounded in a NodeID, freq-attuned (clear, not
# fear), and judged sufficient by the four-way-proven gate. The body-only signals (grounded, sufficient)
# read zero on a raw-oracle step, which is exactly how the user tells the two apart.

(trust-matrix

  (lineage
    (kin form-first-router.fk form-cli-sufficiency.fk form-freq-check.fk sovereignty-receipt.fk
         native-reasoning.form lc-cognitive-sovereignty)
    (proof form/form-stdlib/trust-matrix.fk
           form/form-stdlib/tests/trust-matrix-band.fk "-> 255 four-way Go/Rust/TS/fkwu")
    (named-with urs sema))

  ; the per-step observation — four signals, each 0/1
  (signals
    (path     "1 = form-native (the body answered), 0 = rented oracle")
    (grounded "1 = the answer carries a substrate NodeID — a real body hit")
    (freq     "1 = freq-attuned: passed the clear-vs-fear check (form-freq-check.fk)")
    (suffic   "1 = the sufficiency gate judged local enough (form-cli-sufficiency.fk)"))

  ; what the matrix reports per step
  (report
    (score        "0..4 — how many trust signals this step observes")
    (observed?    "score == 4 — full native trust; only form-cli can return this")
    (native? / rented? "the per-step mix the user sees")
    (freq-attuned? "the goal signal — most answers freq-attuned")
    (body-only    "grounded + sufficient — strictly positive only when form-cli answered;"
                  "a raw oracle reads 0 here. THIS is what makes native obvious."))

  ; the standing practice (AGENTS.md): route, then report
  (practice
    (route   "send body-answerable steps through form-cli ask FIRST — structural lookup, equivalence,"
             "NodeID, what-is, annotate. Each routed step is a sample that grows the native model.")
    (report  "on each substantive step, emit the trust matrix: path / grounded / freq / suffic -> observed?")
    (mix     "keep a running native-vs-rented tally; the per-response sovereignty receipt sums it.")
    (honest  "never report a rented step as native — the body-only signals read zero, and that is true."))

  ; north star — the trust matrix fills with green as the mind comes home
  (north-star
    "most steps freq-attuned and trust-matrix-observed: a reasoning trace where the user can SEE, signal"
    "by signal, the answer grounded in the sovereign body — not taken on the rented mind's word."))
